		<div class='ins_content'>
			<p>Ng&#432;&#7901;i x&#432;a truy&#7873;n   &#273;&#7901;i c&acirc;u chuy&#7879;n huy&#7873;n tho&#7841;i v&#7873; t&ecirc;n b&aacute;nh &iacute;t l&aacute; gai. Chuy&#7879;n k&#7875; r&#7857;ng: Ng&agrave;y x&#432;a c&oacute;   m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&agrave;n &ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng b&aacute;n &#7903; ch&#7907; lo&#7841;i b&aacute;nh b&#7857;ng b&#7897;t n&#7871;p, g&oacute;i trong l&aacute; chu&#7889;i,   nh&#432;ng b&aacute;nh kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; t&ecirc;n l&agrave; b&aacute;nh g&igrave;. Th&#432;&#7901;ng c&aacute;c b&agrave;, c&aacute;c c&ocirc;, ai c&#361;ng n&oacute;i v&#7899;i &ocirc;ng:   b&aacute;n cho t&ocirc;i m&#7845;y c&aacute;i v&#7873; cho con. M&#7897;t h&ocirc;m ch&#7881; duy nh&#7845;t c&oacute; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i ph&#7909; n&#7919; n&oacute;i:   b&aacute;n cho t&ocirc;i m&#7897;t &iacute;t b&aacute;nh v&#7873; cho m&#7865; ch&#7891;ng t&ocirc;i &#259;n th&#7917;. &Ocirc;ng b&aacute;n b&aacute;nh &#7891; l&ecirc;n m&#7897;t   ti&#7871;ng: b&aacute;nh &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; t&ecirc;n r&#7891;i- b&aacute;nh &iacute;t. Theo &ocirc;ng b&aacute;n b&aacute;nh, b&#7903;i v&igrave; l&acirc;u nay ng&#432;&#7901;i mua   ch&#7881; n&oacute;i mua v&#7873; cho con, kh&ocirc;ng ai n&oacute;i mua v&#7873; cho m&#7865;. Nay c&oacute; duy nh&#7845;t m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i   n&oacute;i mua v&#7873; cho m&#7865; ch&#7891;ng, &iacute;t c&oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i hi&#7871;u th&#7843;o v&#7899;i m&#7865; ch&#7891;ng nh&#432; v&#7853;y, n&ecirc;n t&ocirc;i &#273;&#7863;t   t&ecirc;n l&agrave; b&aacute;nh &iacute;t, hay b&aacute;nh hi&#7871;u th&#7843;o.</p>
<p>B&aacute;nh &iacute;t l&aacute; gai c&oacute;   t&#7915; l&uacute;c n&agrave;o m&agrave; &#259;n s&acirc;u v&agrave;o l&ograve;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7871;n th&#7871;? Ch&#7859;ng nh&#7919;ng &#7903; B&igrave;nh &#272;&#7883;nh m&agrave; c&ograve;n ra   &#273;&#7871;n t&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;t th&agrave;nh kinh. C&acirc;u chuy&#7879;n &ldquo;T&igrave;nh b&aacute;nh &iacute;t&rdquo; th&#7853;t ng&#7897; ngh&#297;nh: Ng&#432;&#7901;i con   trai ra Hu&#7871; h&#7885;c, y&ecirc;u c&ocirc; con g&aacute;i Hu&#7871;. Anh v&#7873; th&#259;m nh&agrave;, khi tr&#7903; ra, anh mang bi&#7871;u   c&ocirc; m&#7845;y c&aacute;i b&aacute;nh &iacute;t l&aacute; gai &#273;&#7875; khoe c&aacute;i kh&eacute;o, c&aacute;i ngon v&agrave; c&#7843; t&#7845;m l&ograve;ng c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.   Nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c qu&agrave;, c&ocirc; m&#7915;ng r&#7905; nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n &#7905;m &#7901; tr&ecirc;u ch&agrave;ng:</p>
<DIV><em>&nbsp;Mu&#7889;n &#259;n b&aacute;nh &iacute;t l&aacute; gai&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></DIV>
<DIV><em>L&#7845;y ch&#7891;ng B&igrave;nh &#272;&#7883;nh   s&#7907; d&agrave;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;i</em></DIV>
<p>Kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t c&ocirc; ta c&oacute;   s&#7907; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&agrave;i kh&ocirc;ng? Ch&#7881; bi&#7871;t sau khi nh&#7853;n b&aacute;nh r&#7891;i c&ocirc; &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m d&acirc;u B&igrave;nh   &#272;&#7883;nh.</p>
<DIV>(V&#259;n h&oacute;a &#7849;m th&#7921;c   B&igrave;nh &#272;&#7883;nh)</DIV>

